None shall trespass the Heart of Water! Nomak samman vanan vâdâyyâ khâ!
All shall surrender to the flow! Nohm vâdâyyâ khattah!
None shall trespass the Heart of Earth! Nomak samman vanan khâvîddhi khâ!
All shall surrender to the weight! Nohm khâvîddhi khattah!
None shall trespass the Heart of Wind! Nomak samman vanan vâyyâbeh khâ!
All shall surrender to the tempest! Nohm vâyyâbeh khattah!
All shall surrender to the flow! Nohm vâdâyyâ khattah!
Who dares to desecrate this holy place!? Nomak samman vanan vâdâyyâ khâ!
All shall surrender to the tempest! Nohm vâyyâbeh khattah!
Defend the tamate-bako of geomancy! Nomak samman vanan vâyyâbeh khâ!

Yea, you who are not geomancers must die this day!
The covenant demands it!
The flames are mine to command! To control!
I yet burn with divinity!
At last, after centuries, I am unbound...
HIE YOU FROM THIS SACRED PLACE!
THE LAND TAKE YOU, CLAIM YOU!
SWALLOW YOU, CONSUME YOU!
THE LAND, THE LAND, THE LAND...
Oho, a challenge! Let us dance, you and I!
Mine is a most unique weapon! Observe!
Ah, but it would be unfair not to let the others join the fun!
Will my rod have the last word?
Apparently not! Then for my final trick...

Is emptiness form, or form emptiness?
Either way, I am still here and hitting you!
Heehee HAHA hahaha HEEHEE haha HEEEEEE!!!
THE RECKONING COMES!!!
Die! DIE!!! DIIIIIIEEE!!!
My power... No...
HOWL, TEMPEST! NONE SHALL ESCAPE MY WRATH!
Thy soul shall burn for eternity!
My flames shall consume thy flesh and soul both!
Surrender thyself to the fires of judgment!
The blessing of Light...defies me!?
The flames hunger for thee, mortal!
Tremble before the might of the earth!
Sons of man! Murderers of my children!
For thee my hatred is unending, unyielding!
Hie, my children, into the dark! <If(PlayerParameter(4))>She<Else/>He</If> will not be denied...
All my fury I shall bring to bear against thy kind!
Your tale ends here, Warrior of Light!
You but delay the inevitable.

It seems the champion of Hydaelyn is not so easily cowed.
Let us see how you fare against the Ultima Weapon!
From the deepest pit of the seven hells to the very pinnacle of the heavens, the world shall tremble! Unleash Ultima!
Ahahaha! Nothing can save you now!
See how the Heart of Sabik pulses with primal energy!

Arrive in the Clockwork Coliseum
Long has it been since I last gazed upon the open sky...and the vermin who scurry beneath her.
With this vessel shall your doom be met.
O darkest of vessels! You are my sword! You are my rain!
O darkest of vessels! You are my bow! You are my rain!
Behold as waters most foul spill forth to defile the land!
Let the crashing waves cleanse you of your sins!
Let the crashing waves bear you into the abyss!
From brine are we born, unto brine shall we return.
In darkness will you know true fear!
The night...beckons once more...

You will pay for what you have done...with blood!
Scream louder! I want to remember this!

Children of war, I am Belias.
Come! Warm your hands at my fire!
That your wrath...might eclipse mine...
You cannot withstand my rage!
Time waits for no one!
Bound by the march of time, forevermore!
All hands point to death!
Rise, loyal minions. Heed my call!
Step into the inferno! Step into my hellfire!
Are you not yet ash and bone!?
INCREASING DIFFICULTY...

OVERHEAT ALERT!
OVERHEAT ALERT!
CHARGING COOLING UNITS.
The Empire is a cancer, and I am the barber's blade!
Feel the wrath of my brothers!
You will not know mercy!
Like a knife through butter!
My wounds...give me strength!
We will discover Ba'Gamnan here within the lighthouse. I am certain of it.
Did Ba'Gamnan─the Duma─give life to that creature!?
The seal on the gate is lifted. We can now venture further up the lighthouse.
This pattern... It is unmistakably─ No, it cannot be...
The city remains functional...after all these centuries. Let us access the transportation nodes.
The city's defenses also seem operational. Destroy them, if you must.
The heat...is almost unbearable. Could this be the heart of the lighthouse's beacon?
I've discovered another device.
The architecture here is similar to that of the lighthouse...yet something feels off. The air...is so thin...
I believe you've succeeded in clearing another path.
Those golems... I believe I now know where we are!
The area's final line of defense is upon us. We must proceed with the utmost caution!
There is no mistaking it. We are in the legendary Clockwork City of Goug!
Oh...it's going to be a long night.
Let's share the torment, shall we...?

Enough of that.
I wouldn't want the pain to grow familiar.

Struggle all you wish─I encourage it!
Your death will be all the sweeter...
Why does it fade away...?

Worthless excuse for a daughter.
You're nothing but trouble.
A font of misery, that's what you are!

Fight like your life depends on it, dear sister.
You wouldn't want to disappoint me...

If it isn't the cold-blooded little worm.
Always crawling through my rotten heart.
Your pitiful fortunes can bring you no lower...
Stay behind me, Tsuyu!

Why...?
You have no place here...

Perhaps... But it is too late for me.
There can be no redemption.
All is bitterness and ashes...
In darkness blooms the spider lily...
From mortal husk I rise anew!
Suffused with night, I shall prevail!
In moonlight's chill, shine petals pale...
In sunless gloom, black tendrils trail...

Rising moon!
A light without warmth, stark and uncaring!

Reaping crescent!
A sweeping doom, striking from darkness!

No. No... Not yet.
Not. Yet.

Yes, my dearest parents.
I was the bane of your existence unto the very end!

The waning moon commands the night.
Its light...and its darkness!

This is far from over!
My bloodied hands have much left to accomplish!
A nightbloom shall flower here upon the site of my demise...
A nightbloom shall flower here upon the graves of my enemies!

You have come to deliver judgment for my failure?
Cut me down, then. Surely it is a simple task!

The stalks are cast, and the fates have spoken.
There will be no dawn for Doma─only night unending.

You must survive, Tsuyu!
The kami spared us, and we cannot repay that boon in death!

A tiresome contest.
Begone from my sight!
Am I sunk to my lowest, then...?

...Ah. I understand.
It feeds on my spite. On my suffering...

Come forth, shades of the dead! Curse my name!
Strike my body! Fill my soul with blackest malice!
Search for survivors.
Destroy the airship wreckage.
Use Physick to heal the wounded soldier.
Defeat the enemy commander.
Defeat the enemy.
Revive the wounded soldier.

Master Alphinaud, might I ask you to search for survivors?
I will see to our injured helmsmen.

My thanks...
I don't think I would have made it...

Yes, you very likely saved his life.
The question of who would try to take it remains, however...

Put these last few out of their misery.
The prince wishes none left alive!
The prince...!?

They've not come to parley, I fear...
Ready your weapons!
A fine display.

By the Emperor, that man is a fiend!
Cross formation! Deploy restraints!

The dragon dissolves into mist.
Striking the mist is futile! To do so only incurs the dragon's wrath!
Destroy the draconic regards to force the beast to reform!
The mist is coalescing! Strike now!
The dragon disappears into the mist.
The dragon is poised to swoop! Be on your guard!

Arrive in Kingsloam
Tenzen? Tenzen, 'tis I! Sheathe your sword, I beg of you!
You gave me the strength to rise from the ashes!
I never showed you my true form, did I...?
Tenzen, please!
Why do you do this!?
All I ever wanted was for you and I to...to...
You never did make it easy, did you?
We will wake you from this madness!
I could not bear to lose you again!
Trust in me, my love! I will protect you─I promise!
Please, my love─ If only you would listen...
Hearken to my melody...
Do not fight it, my love. Let me into your heart...
If it must be thus, then I'm glad...it is you...
Let there be no more secrets between us...
Hearken to my melody...

Grovel in terror!
The flames hunger for your flesh!

Scurry and flail, little mortals!
The raging tide will claim you all!

Despair at your hollow fate!
The winds will strip away your skin!

Hark, wretched creatures!
The earth itself rumbles of your doom!
Tremble before the might of a god!

The crystal...destroyed!?
YOU DARE!

Abandon this feeble hope.
None may rise above me!

You are the Alpha, I am the Omega.

Come, khagan! Let us dance!
You are strong indeed... A worthy champion of the Steppe...
But you are mistaken if you think I will fall so easily!
Ahhh, fighting you is pure bliss!
Such sweet pleasure, I will not suffer to end so soon!
...Well? Do not tell me that is all you have?
My soul demands more, khagan! Give me more!
\\<grunt> My arms...grow heavy... My eyes dim...
But so long as my lifeblood flows...I will fight on!
Yaaaaaarrrgh!
Come! Let us begin anew!
This is the reckoning, khagan! One must fall!
60 seconds to Meteor impact...
30 seconds to Meteor impact...
20 seconds to Meteor impact...
10 seconds to Meteor impact...
5 seconds to Meteor impact...
Come! Plead your case unto the Sun!
Oh, we shall endeavor to be most convincing!
When we have claimed victory, I claim Hien for the Buduga!
\\<sigh> Do as you will...
Focus on Magnai─leave Daidukul to me.
You, too, must learn your place.
You have left yourself open, Doman!

My fist swells with the passion of the Buduga!
Every last drop, I give to you, Hien!
Ugh, this bodes ill... Y'shtola─some healing would be welcome!
So you still stand. But soon you will kneel.
Know the folly of opposing the will of Azim!
These axes will not break! You have nowhere to hide!
Very well, then... Y'shtola─to me!
I shall take care of this!
What!?
Every step you will take, every move you will make─the Sun sees all!
Now, fall!
Ungh... What strength─what grace is this?
Let's move this right along!
Hmph, predictable!
Time to finish this!

So it is you...
You will not defile my new paradise!
Scurrying about my domain like insects... I will not suffer it!
Come no closer, filthy creatures!
I am righteousness!
And righteousness will prevail!
Bah, can't you do anything by yourselves!?
Very well, if you will not be discouraged...
Stop them, damn you! I don't care what it takes!
Defeat the forgiven obscenity

Come forth, my child!
Feast upon the flesh of impudent mortals!
From the heart of the eldest star doth weep the light of oblivion!

I am Midgardsormr.
Father of Dragons, and paragon of wyrms!

Thou and thine fight with admirable spirit.
I reward such courage with an exchange on even ground...

Valiantly have you struggled, but no more.
My roar shall herald your downfall!
My coils will confound your mortal eyes...

'Tis the fate of all dragons to shed one form for another.
Even in battle are mine assaults ever-changing!

Overlong doth this clash endure.
Let us not allow the dance to grow stale!

I am the Omega and the Alpha.
I will mimic your weakness to comprehend your strength.

The time has come and so have I!
I...I did not expect such fierce opposition! And from eight of you, no less!

Enough! It is time we fought like men.
And ladies. And men who dress like ladies!
For Yojimbo... It is Gilgameshing time!
Yes, 'tis I! The man, the myth, the legend!
Divide and conquer, Gilgamesh style!

I have learned much and more in the
Far East, my friends! Behold!
Double your pleasure! Double your fun!
Look behind you! A giant me!
How our hearts sing in the chaos!

You have some skill, I'll give you that...
But Gilgamesh has only just begun to fight!
What's the matter, friend? All tied up?
Take wing, ye souls of war!
Slippery little devil, aren't you!?

Most impressive! Very well!
I, too, shall fight with all my strength!
I...I will not be bested yet again! Have at thee!

They will not escape.
Commence bombardment, and prepare to strike.
Impressive. Annia, let us engage them together.
They cannot hope to evade us both.
Annia. Fall back.
Very well. Leave the artillery to me.
Ready the ceruleum tanks.
Deploying now.
You should feel honored, savages. Few are they who have witnessed this twice.
It seems we have no choice, Julia.
And fewer still who have witnessed this...
Farewell, savages.
Annia. Take the field.
Very well. I leave the artillery fire to you.

The aether grows thick. She whom we seek must lie beyond this threshold.
My name is Mustadio Bunansa...and all paths lead through me.
Nothing I cannot fix!
And where might you be off to?
You have proven yourself deserving of the title, Zodiac Brave. With this my journey can, at long last, come to an end.
The Beoulve youth guides your fate, but have you the faith to fulfill his legacy?
Well fought, champion. I leave you now to your quest. My Ovelia awaits...
Witness as the light returns!
Spirits of heroes fallen, rise! Pass thy judgment on those who would gaze unto the beyond!

Bend to my will!
An inescapable prison awaits!
Graaaaaah!
To the current of life we succumb, its judgment swift and final. Its bite as cold as steel.
The hearts of men are black with corruption and must needs be cleansed!
Seven shadows cast, seven fates foretold. Yet at the end of the broken path lies death, and death alone.
I call out to the skies and tremble as the brilliance of a thousand bolts blinds mine enemies and tears their flesh asunder.
They who dwell aloft have spoken. Let their words echo in your empty soul. Ruination is come!
The dreams of men are fleeting, yet they must be embraced if they are to flourish. Have you the faith to do as much?
Gaze deep into the light!
O, divine light! Send us from our sins!
Raise your shields against the falling light!
Raise your swords against the coming night!
You shall rue the day you raised your eyes to the heavens.
Denizens of the abyss! From ink of blackest night, I summon you!
I see it now. In you...his blood, my vanquisher in times...long past. But not so soon...shall I accept defeat...
O darkest of vessels! You are my sword! You are my rain!
Time waits for no one!
To maintain order, one must first have control.
Honed is the blade that severs the villain's head. Endless is the path that leads him from hell.
It is time to end this!
Bare your steel!
Simmer does the light of life before rising to the heavens in a cleansing conflagration of divine benevolence.
She weaves her foul magicks!
Only we can shield you from doom! To me, heroes! To me!
You will not intervene!
What is she doing!?
The barrier will not last! We must stop her!
Is it over?
I am the only god!
Such fury!
Now is not the time to stay our blades!
Children of Hydaelyn! Make it swift! You are Her only hope!
Few can claim to have endured the might of my will.
Your coming was foretold, servant of Ivalice. Or perhaps you serve another.
I am Count Cidolfus Orlandeau. Your journey ends here.
The clouds have parted and the skies cleared. It is time I bade you farewell.
To the current of life we succumb, its judgment swift and final. Its bite as cold as steel.
The hearts of men are black with corruption and must needs be cleansed!
